-- Southampton Earns Premier League Promotion by Beating Coventry
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-04-28T13:22:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-28/southampton-earns-premier-league-promotion-by-beating-coventry.html
Southampton defeated Coventry 4-0
to secure promotion to English soccer’s Premier League.  Southampton’s victory on the final day of the season
clinches second place in the second-tier Championship behind
Reading. The top two teams in the league gain automatic
promotion to the Premier League.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  